(27, 1, '2012-08-20 03:25:17', '2012-08-20 03:25:17', '<div class="roastParagraphBox">\n<p class="paragraph">Brooklyn isn’t known for being mild but we’ve toned it down a little for our BBR Light roast to produce an impeccably balanced coffee with a light, crisp taste. It has a full body and character with a hint of robust nutty overtones but it is light-bodied flavor with a mild finish and aroma.</p>\n\n<h1>Enjoy this mellow blend and take in the lighter side of Brooklyn.</h1>\n</div>\n<div class="roastTypeImageBox">\n\n[caption id="attachment_76" align="alignleft" width="89"]<a class="fancyBox" href="#breakfast-blend"><img class="size-full wp-image-76  " title="Caps_LightRoasts_Regular" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta//////wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Caps_LightRoasts_Regular.png" alt="" width="89" height="87" /></a> Breakfast Blend[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_77" align="alignleft" width="89"]<a class="fancyBox" href="#breakfast-blend-decaf"><img class="size-full wp-image-77  " title="Caps_LightRoasts_Decaf" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta//////wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Caps_LightRoasts_Decaf.png" alt="" width="89" height="87" /></a> Breakfast Blend Decaf[/caption]\n\n</div>', 'Light Roasts', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-autosave', '', '', '2012-08-20 03:25:17', '2012-08-20 03:25:17', '', 15, 'http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta//////?p=27', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(28, 1, '2012-08-17 02:15:31', '2012-08-17 02:15:31', '<div class="roastParagraphBox">\n<p class="paragraph">In Brooklyn, we know bold. (or In Brooklyn we know a thing or two about being bold) And when we say this coffee is bold you betta believe it’s bold. To get a perfect dark roast, the beans are removed from the roasters right before they become “espresso roasts” so they retain sharp floral notes and all the smoky goodness without any of the burnt aftertaste. When these beans with big-time flavor are brewed through our patented tension based filters they create a cup of Joe that will delight lovers of good strong coffee. The Brooklyn Bean rich &amp; robust dark roasts are as strong and intense as the borough they come from.</p>\n\n<h1>So go ahead, its Brooklyn… Be bold!</h1>\n</div>\n<div class="roastTypeImageBox">\n\n[caption id="attachment_274" align="alignleft" width="89"]<a href="#cyclone"><img class="size-full wp-image-274" title="cyclone" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta///wp-content/uploads/2012/07/cyclone.png" alt="" width="89" height="87" /></a> Cyclone[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_275" align="alignleft" width="89"]<a href="#fuhgeddabouit"><img class="size-full wp-image-275" title="fughet" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta///wp-content/uploads/2012/07/fughet.png" alt="" width="89" height="87" /></a> Fuhgeddaboutit[/caption]\n\n</div>', 'Dark Roasts', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-autosave', '', '', '2012-08-17 02:15:31', '2012-08-17 02:15:31', '', 17, 'http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta//////?p=28', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(29, 1, '2012-08-17 05:56:50', '2012-08-17 05:56:50', '<div class="roastParagraphBox">\n<p class="paragraph">Like standing in a subway car and holding on to the above-the-head grab bar, making a great medium roast requires a bit of a balancing act. You want to get a strong, rich flavor that stays smooth and has a very even texture all at the same time. Each of the Brooklyn Bean mediums are specially crafted to bring out perfect balance of crisp nuttiness and full bodied smoky flavor for the most extraordinary tasting stuff in a cup.</p>\n\n<h1>There are very few things that Brooklyn does halfway. Lucky for you, a good medium roast coffee is one of them. Enjoy!</h1>\n</div>\n<div class="roastTypeImageBox">\n\n[caption id="attachment_271" align="alignleft" width="89"]<a class="fancyBox" href="#brooklyn-bridge-blend"><img class="size-full wp-image-271   " title="brooklynBridge" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta///wp-content/uploads/2012/07/brooklynBridge.png" alt="" width="89" height="87" /></a> Brooklyn Bridge Blend[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_272" align="alignleft" width="89"]<a class="fancyBox" href="#columbian"><img class="size-full wp-image-272  " title="columbian" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta///wp-content/uploads/2012/07/columbian.png" alt="" width="89" height="87" /></a> Columbian[/caption]\n\n</div>', 'Medium Roasts', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '16-autosave', '', '', '2012-08-17 05:56:50', '2012-08-17 05:56:50', '', 16, 'http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta//////?p=29', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
