(374, 1, '2012-09-12 05:02:44', '2012-09-12 05:02:44', '<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-460" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 410px;" title="car" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta//wp-content/uploads/2012/08/car2-300x140.png" alt="" width="300" height="140" />\n\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-609" title="hazelnut" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta//wp-content/uploads/2012/08/hazelnut.png" alt="" width="170" height="170" />\n<h2>I''m nuts for _______</h2>\n<p class="paragraph">What''s the difference between a hazelnut and a filbert? Nada. Hazelnut = Filbert, but “Filbert Coffee” did not go over well with our focus groups.</p>\n<p class="paragraph">Who wants some free Filb – I mean Hazelnut coffee? Fill in the quote, “I’m NUTS for_____________!” for your chance at a free box! All entries are also eligible for our Grand Prize – free coffee for one year! Guess what? You also can buy it right now on Amazon. To submit log onto our <a title="FB page" href="http://www.facebook.com/BrooklynBeanRoastery">FB page</a></p>\n<p class="paragraph fancybox"><a href="#hazelnut">Contest Rules</a></p>\n<p class="paragraph fancybox contest-breakers">These are the rules.</p>\n\n\n<hr />\n\n<img class="size-full wp-image-427 alignleft" title="placeholder" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta//wp-content/uploads/2012/08/placeholder.png" alt="" width="170" height="170" />\n<h2>Show Us Your Skyline</h2>\n<p class="paragraph">"Did you know? If you request a ‘latte’ in Italy, you’ll get a glass of milk? Did you also know if you upload an image of your skyline to our Facebook page, you’ll be entered to win a free box of Vanilla Skyline coffee for your single cup coffee make AND (yes, AND) could win our Grand Prize: one-year of free coffee? And if you tag a friend in your photo, you both could win a free box?!</p>\n<p class="paragraph">We know. We just blew your mind."                                                      <span style="color: #ff6600; font-size: medium;"> This contest is now over 8/15/12</span></p>\n<p class="paragraph"><a href="#skylineRules">Contest Rules</a></p>\n<p class="contest-breakers"><span class="paragraph">Upload YOUR skyline image for a chance to win a free box of this amazing Keurig-compatible coffee. Tag your buddy in the photo and they could get coffee, too, and you are both eligible to win the Grand Prize – free coffee for an entire year! Wanna get your hands on this coffee now? Buy on Amazon.</span>\n<span class="paragraph">Winners please send your shipping address (even if you think we have it) to info@brooklynbeans.com so that we can send out your free box of Vanilla Skyline.</span></p>\n\n\n<hr />\n\n<img class="alignleft  wp-image-425" title="lia-resized" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta//wp-content/uploads/2012/08/lia-resized.png" alt="" width="170" height="170" />\n<h2>Like Us on <a title="Facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/BrooklynBeanRoastery">Facebook</a></h2>\n<p class="paragraph">We would like to raise a mug in salute to Brooklyn native Lia Neal. She is the 2nd African American to qualify for the US Olympic Swim Team. On Saturday she won a bronze medal in Women''s 4x100m Freestyle Relay.</p>\n<p class="paragraph">Who would you like to raise a mug in salute to? Just by answering you will automatically be entered to win a draw for a free sampler pack. There will be a 2nd draw for people who tag the person they are saluting. <a href="http://www.facebook.com/BrooklynBeanRoastery">http://www.facebook.com/BrooklynBeanRoastery</a>                                 <span style="color: #ff6600; font-size: medium;">This contest is now  over 8/3/12</span></p>\n\n\n<hr />\n\n<img class="alignleft  wp-image-378" title="groupon" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta///wp-content/uploads/2012/08/groupon.jpg" alt="" width="170" height="170" />\n<h2><strong>Only 5 Days Left to HUGE Groupon Sale.</strong></h2>\n<p class="paragraph">Don’t miss out on this one! <a title="http://www.groupon.com/" href="http://www.groupon.com/">http://www.groupon.com/</a>                                      <span style="color: #ff6600; font-size: medium;">This promotion is now over</span></p>\n&nbsp;', 'Contests & Promotions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '123-autosave', '', '', '2012-09-12 05:02:44', '2012-09-12 05:02:44', '', 123, 'http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta///?p=374', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
