(396, 1, '2012-08-14 22:27:54', '2012-08-14 22:27:54', '<h2><img class="size-full wp-image-240 alignright" title="About-the-Company" src="http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta////wp-content/uploads/2012/08/About-the-Co.png" alt="Brooklyn Bean Roastery" width="317" height="510" /></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Shouldn’t every cup of coffee taste as fresh as the first cup of the day?</strong></h2>\r\n<p class="paragraph">That’s what we believe at Brooklyn Bean Roastery.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class="paragraph">Founded in 2010, Brooklyn Bean has become a pioneer in introducing Keurig-compatible filtered single serve coffee cups to market. Decades of experience in product engineering led to the design of our unique tension-based filtered technology, ensuring that every cup of coffee tastes as good and as fresh as the first.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="paragraph">\r\n	<li>Compatible with all Keurig brewers &amp; brewed using our patent pending tension based filter system</li>\r\n	<li>Revolutionary roast2cup process ensures a smooth and rich cup of coffee every time.</li>\r\n	<li>Extra fresh and filter brewed, using only the highest quality 100% Arabica Coffee</li>\r\n	<li>A more affordable alternative to Green Mountain without compromising on the quality of the coffee</li>\r\n	<li>Brooklyn Bean Roastery will introduce a full tea and cocoa line in late 2012</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;', 'About the Company', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '120-revision-8', '', '', '2012-08-14 22:27:54', '2012-08-14 22:27:54', '', 120, 'http://www.brooklynbeans.com/beta//?p=396', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
